# Project Overview

This is a React Router v7 application with TypeScript, Prisma for database management, and Vite for build tooling.

## Main Entry Points
- [app/root.tsx](mdc:app/root.tsx) - The root component of the application
- [app/entry.client.tsx](mdc:app/entry.client.tsx) - Client-side entry point
- [app/entry.server.tsx](mdc:app/entry.server.tsx) - Server-side entry point

## Core Directories
- `app/assets/` - Static assets (images, icons) that are directly imported and used in the application code
- `app/components/` - Reusable React components
- `app/i18n` - Multi-language translation files
- `app/lib` - Support constants and functions
- `app/models/` - Data models and business logic
- `app/routes/` - Contains all route components
- `app/styles` - Shared CSS files
- `app/utils/` - Utility functions and helpers
- `cypress/` - Cypress tests
- `prisma/` - Database schema and migrations

## Configuration Files
- [react-router-config.js](mdc:react-router-config.js) - Remix configuration
- [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) - Vite build configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) - Database schema definition
